---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Us - Türkel Global Stands"
  description="With our expert team in exhibition stand design and production, we represent your brand in the strongest way. Together with our technical team, we determine the most suitable participation model for your needs and manage your process with an innovative and comprehensive approach."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy text-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center animate-on-scroll">
        <h1 class="text-h4 font-hanken font-medium mb-4">
          About Us
        </h1>
        <p class="text-body text-white/80 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          With our expert team in exhibition stand design and production, we represent your brand in the strongest way. 
          Together with our technical team, we determine the most suitable participation model for your needs and 
          manage your process with an innovative and comprehensive approach.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Content -->
  <section class="py-section-lg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-start px-4 md:px-0">
        <!-- Left Image -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 animate-on-scroll">
          <img 
            src="/about-image.jpg" 
            alt="Türkel Global Stands About Us" 
            class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg max-w-md mx-auto lg:mx-0"
            loading="lazy"
            width="1024"
            height="1024"
          />
        </div>
        
        <!-- Right Content -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-3 space-y-8">
          <div class="animate-on-scroll">
            <h2 class="text-xl md:text-h4 font-semibold text-black mb-4 md:mb-6">
              Your Reliable Solution Partner in Custom Stand Designs
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6 text-body text-grey">
              <p>
                As Türkel Global Stands, we are with you at every stage of your exhibition process. 
                Together with our technical team, we determine the most suitable participation model for your needs 
                and manage your process with an innovative and comprehensive approach.
              </p>
              
              <p>
                We make a difference with our advanced R&D studies, original designs, effective production and 
                fast assembly post-services. Our goal is to provide the highest satisfaction to our customers 
                in every project and to represent your brand in the strongest way in the exhibition area.
              </p>

              <p>
                We provide exhibition stand design, production and installation services in European countries 
                such as Germany, France, Netherlands, Italy, Spain; and Arab countries such as United Arab Emirates, 
                Saudi Arabia, Qatar, Kuwait and Bahrain. We take part in international projects in these regions 
                with strong collaborations.
              </p>

              <p>
                With our experience of over 30 years, as one of Turkey's leading exhibition stand design and 
                production companies, we carry out successful projects in national and international projects.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision Section -->
  <section class="py-section-lg bg-cream">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Section Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="section-heading mb-6">
            Mission & Vision
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body text-grey max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            With our vision and mission in the exhibition industry, we aim to provide the best service to our customers.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-12 px-4 md:px-0">
          <!-- Mission Card -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4 md:mb-6">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 bg-orange rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 md:mr-4">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h4 font-semibold text-navy">Our Mission</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-body text-grey leading-relaxed">
              To provide the highest quality design and production services to exhibition participants, 
              ensuring that their brands are represented most effectively in the exhibition area. 
              To be a leader in the sector with creative solutions and professional service approach, 
              keeping customer satisfaction at the forefront.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Vision Card -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 bg-navy rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 md:mr-4">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 md:w-6 md:h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h4 font-semibold text-navy">Our Vision</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-body text-grey leading-relaxed">
              As Turkey's leading exhibition stand design and production company, to become a recognized 
              brand in the international arena. With our continuous innovation and development approach, 
              we aim to provide competitive quality service in the global market.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="py-section-lg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Section Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16 animate-on-scroll px-4 md:px-0">
          <h2 class="section-heading mb-6">
            Our Values
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 px-4 md:px-0">
          <!-- Value 1 -->
          <div class="text-center animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 md:mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h5 font-semibold text-navy mb-2 md:mb-3">Quality</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey">
              We provide design and production services at the highest quality standards.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Value 2 -->
          <div class="text-center animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 md:mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h5 font-semibold text-navy mb-2 md:mb-3">On-Time Delivery</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey">
              We complete your projects within the specified time and adapt to your exhibition schedules.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Value 3 -->
          <div class="text-center animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 md:mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h5 font-semibold text-navy mb-2 md:mb-3">Creativity</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey">
              We make your brand stand out with original and creative designs.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Value 4 -->
          <div class="text-center animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 md:mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h5 font-semibold text-navy mb-2 md:mb-3">Customer Focus</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey">
              We provide personalized solutions by understanding customer needs.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Value 5 -->
          <div class="text-center animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 md:mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h5 font-semibold text-navy mb-2 md:mb-3">Reliability</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey">
              We establish reliable business partnerships by standing behind our promises.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Value 6 -->
          <div class="text-center animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 md:mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-h5 font-semibold text-navy mb-2 md:mb-3">Global Perspective</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-grey">
              We compete in the global market by providing services at international standards.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
